==Amateur Radio==

I am SV1XV, more information about my amateur radio activities is available at QRZ.COM [http://www.qrz.com/sv1xv]

==Wikipedia==
I am trying to contribute to and improve the following WP projects:

* [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Amateur radio]]
* [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Military history]]: Editing articles about traditional (pre-1990) military radio communications systems and equipment. I also tag relevant radio communications articles (stations, equipment) for WPMILHIST and associated task forces.

I also own quite a few books on radio related subjects (mostly in english and a few in german) and I try to insert book references in related WP articles & Wikibooks.

