== Look at the package MultiSeries ==

Note that exp(1/x^2) is not analytic at x=0. Anyways, more general asymptotic scales can be used with the commands of the MultiSeries package. In particular, 

 with(MultiSeries);
 series(exp(1/x^2), x);
             exp(1/x^2)

[[User:Jakubi|Jakubi]] ([[User talk:Jakubi|talk]]) 02:11, 20 May 2008 (UTC)

