==== difftime ====

{{C++ Programming/Syntax|
<source lang=cpp>
#include <ctime>
double difftime( time_t time2, time_t time1 );
</source>
}}

The function difftime() returns ''time2'' - ''time1'', in seconds.

;Related topics: [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/asctime|asctime]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/gmtime|gmtime]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/localtime|localtime]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/time|time]]

