Once you have satisfied these requirements, send me a message and I can rename you. If you have any questions, or if you need any help, you can ask me on [[User talk:Whiteknight|my user talk page]], or you can ask the community at [[WB:CHAT]] or [[WB:AN]]. --'''Whiteknight'''&nbsp;([[User:Whiteknight|Page]])&nbsp;([[User talk:Whiteknight|Talk]]) 03:22, 30 May 2008 (UTC)
